-- Old Mutual's First-Half Profit Climbs to $1.2 Billion From Year a Earlier
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-08-06T06:01:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/old-mutual-s-first-half-profit-climbs-to-1-2-billion-from-year-a-earlier.html

          
          
             Old Mutual Plc said its adjusted
operating profit before tax for the six months through June
increased to 735 million pounds from 513 million pounds a year
earlier.  
 Old Mutual commented in an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        